'Dengan karunia Tuhan Krishna'

00:10:17.080 --> 00:10:19.760
'Karn dan Uruvi bersatu'

00:10:20.000 --> 00:10:21.440
'dalam tubuh, pikiran dan jiwa.'

00:10:21.640 --> 00:10:24.920
'Uruvi mendapatkan cinta Radha'

00:10:25.120 --> 00:10:28.640 line:20%
